# Direct dependencies across all apps + the eval harness (the union of the
# per-folder requirements.txt files). This is the INPUT to the lockfile.
#
# Generate a fully pinned, hashed lockfile for reproducible installs with:
#
#     make lock        # -> requirements.lock (pip-compile --generate-hashes)
#
# then install reproducibly with:
#
#     pip install --require-hashes -r requirements.lock
#
# The lockfile is generated on a machine with network access (it resolves the
# full transitive tree against PyPI) and committed; it is NOT produced here.

